{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/logo.png?t=1711505899\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Bloody Ink is a first-person psychological horror game that aims to instill anxiety, distress, and terror.</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_01.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><strong>Luca </strong> is a man who has lost his job. He lives day by day trying to survive. When a new job finally promises to change his life, his nightmare begins. Having to take care of a man who is completely burned, Luca moves into the man's house where the terror becomes real.<br><br>While exploring the house, you will have the task of taking care of the burned man. Discover what caused the fire in which he lost his wife and how all of this is connected to Luca.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_02.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_03.png?t=1711505899\" /><br>Collect items and clues that will help you understand the mystery surrounding the fire.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/001.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_04.png?t=1711505899\" /><br>Darkness is your enemy. Stay in illuminated areas.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/002.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_05.png?t=1711505899\" /><br>The Time Man is hunting you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/003.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_06.png?t=1711505899\" /><br>Solve puzzles and guide Luca to the truth.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/004.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_07.png?t=1711505899\" /><br>In Bloody Ink, the sounds you make influence the game. If you have a microphone, what you say and the sounds you make have an impact on the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/005.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_08.png?t=1711505899\" /><br>Explore the house and the surrounding outer forest.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/006.png?t=1711505899\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/extras/titolo_en_09.png?t=1711505899\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Bloody Ink is designed to terrify and challenge you. Can you find all the hidden easter eggs?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\ud83d\udd26 Collectible Items.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Different game environments.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Psychological mechanics: Fear, Voice Interaction, Madness.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Set in the universe of Lost Alone Ultimate.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Easter Eggs.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Movie Quotes.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Photorealistic environments.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Puzzles.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 Story-related jumpscares and never randomly thrown in. You shouldn't be scared randomly: you should be in constant fear.<br></li><li>\ud83d\udd26 The Time Man is coming...</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"WHO'S THERE?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/c9292cd3267c387054dc805df1bb672b8ae025c3.jpg"},{"name":"CRISPY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/35903aacf38045bd1b4164b206bf140132760103.jpg"},{"name":"ENIGMATIST","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/3974c26adc8f60a58aae6330514852385f5700b6.jpg"},{"name":"OH MY DEER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/791003240f06ed004eef7c6acf2dc1f3a6120c2c.jpg"},{"name":"BLOODY INK","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/ad265605a2ba14d54632bb91b0a4d78fb3276038.jpg"},{"name":"THE MYSTERY MAN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/5959695926e49ed4ffe6b63e501ffb0d1b35ca30.jpg"},{"name":"CHRONOLOGICAL ORDER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/538564a12e27dff4eaef47afaa004dd3d8606348.jpg"},{"name":"EXPERT PROGRAMMER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/cf775fd151eb9312b1e0a2d1bc1a039fbc037d9b.jpg"},{"name":"ART CRITIC","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/f7745ce3a122d1b93a32f8cc224fe0de785a244f.jpg"},{"name":"SUPER PLUMBER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2700240/efece136c32a0bf4a8636eaa1217eeaf045f7612.jpg"}],"total":34},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2700240?t=1711505899","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700240/page_bg_raw.j